Captivating Views from Every Room
With great views from both bedrooms and a glorious bay outlook from the living areas and balcony, this stylish 2-bed, 2-bath corner apartment enjoys easy access to trams, shopping, restaurants and Etihad Stadium sporting events.
Accommodation: Awash with natural light from multiple angles, the open-plan lounge/meals area is serviced by a kitchen featuring Caesarstone surfaces, stainless steel Omega appliances and dishwasher. All complemented by an undercover corner balcony with a glorious outlook towards the spectacular CBD skyline and vast expanses of Port Phillip Bay. A clever interior provides two double bedrooms with mirrored built-in robes which features a master with private ensuite.

Description:
Superb Sub-penthouse style home ready for you to move in!
Perfectly poised high on the 17th floor is this spacious two bedroom two bathroom apartment complete with two side by side carparks in this award winning “Watergate” complex.
Along with fantastic bay, harbour, marina and parkland views, this fantastic apartment also comprises of a gourmet kitchen with a breakfast bar, stainless steel appliances, and stainless steel bench tops. This highly desirable unit is complimented with a large open plan living area, along with a dedicated dining area and opening onto a wide balcony, perfect for entertaining.
Other features of this large home include:
- Two spacious bedrooms, with lavish master bedroom having a walk in robe and a study nook, while the 2nd bedroom has BIR.
- Two secure side by side undercover car parks.
- Secured intercom entry
- Approximately 105sqm of living and terrace space.
Recreational facilities within the Watergate building include a full size swimming pool, Jacuzzi, gym and sauna for residents, with a multi-purpose sports area located just outside the complex.
This is a great opportunity for owner occupiers and investors alike! Location is perfect; with a tram stop being just downstairs, 500 meters from Southern Cross Station, cafes, restaurants and major shopping precincts within a stone's throw.
Don't miss this great opportunity! Please call Peter Doan for more information on 0423 399 999.

Description:
Splendid Light, Superb Space, Exceptional Views
Enjoying astonishing views of the picturesque Victoria Harbour and Port Philip Bay, this superb one bedroom plus large study (spare bedroom) apartment is a delightful combination of natural light, practical open space, and modern style that will be a joy to experience every day.
The 19th floor residence is bathed in natural light and delivers great versatility thanks to the spacious central lounge and meals area and the study which can anything from a home office to another living space or bedroom. An undercover balcony is picture perfect thanks to its westerly aspect and showcases views of the harbour as well as the Melbourne Star Observational Wheel in the distance.
The functional stone kitchen boasts a handy breakfast bar and stainless steel appliances, while the bedroom with built-in robes features balcony access. Other apartment extras include a bathroom with laundry, ducted heating and cooling, and secure intercom entry.
This apartment is positioned in the hugely popular Victoria Point complex, which has access to a concierge and gym. This property is further situated in the outstanding Victoria Harbour precinct, which is a wonderful balance of residential, retail, and office space. It offers great nearby attractions including restaurants and cafes on Bourke Street, Etihad Stadium for sports lovers, terrific eateries on NewQuay Promenade, The Hub @ Docklands with recreation facilities, Docklands Park, trams, and Southern Cross Station.
Please contact Thomas Tregonning on 0413 317 304 to arrange an exclusive viewing.

Description:
Lifestyle, Location and Yarra Point Brilliance
One of the standout offerings in the highly sought-after Yarra Point complex, this memorable two bedroom, two bathroom 12th floor apartment with the added bonus of 2 secure car spaces combines modern and spacious living with unforgettable city and Yarra River views.
Everyday living will be an absolute pleasure as you enjoy the spacious lounge and dining zone, which has a handy study nook adjoining the area as well as the impressive kitchen featuring a stone island bench and stainless steel Miele appliances. The undercover balcony offers amazing city, water, and park views, while both bedrooms have built-in robes including the master bedroom with an elegant ensuite.
Other apartment extras include an immaculate main bathroom with concealed laundry, ducted heating and cooling, video intercom and access to fantastic RekDek facilities which includes a gym, pool, spa, steam room, and sauna. This area is also near fabulous South Wharf restaurants and bars including Common Man and Plus 5 Bar, while other attractions including Direct Factory Outlet, Crown Casino, Melbourne Exhibition Centre, Docklands Park, Spencer Street trams, and Southern Cross Station are all nearby.

Description:
Escape to this Ultra-Modern townhouse with alfresco living.
Graced with remarkable alfresco zones at both the front and the rear and embodying sophisticated townhouse living placing a premium on modern style and relaxed space, this two bedroom residence is a rarely offered opportunity with unmistakable class and 2 car spaces.
Bathed in brilliant light, this amazing double storey property has terrific downstairs living and dining with a gas log fireplace, while an adjoining kitchen is a model of sleek style with stone benchtops and stainless steel appliances. The downstairs level enjoys easy access to the sizeable front entry courtyard and a patio at the rear which offers a tranquil space to enjoy dinners and weekend drinks all year round.
Upstairs is dominated by the two generous bedroom which both come with built-in robes. These bedrooms enjoy terrific privacy and are separated by an ultra-sleek bathroom which has a separate powder room. Other impressive features of this property includes a laundry, reverse cycle heating and cooling, video intercom and 2 secure car spaces.
This wonderful townhouse is located in the NewQuay precinct which is popular for both residents and tourists alike. You’re close to the Melbourne Star Observation Wheel, Waterfront City, Costco, Harbour Town Shopping Centre, and superb restaurants and cafes including Sushi Sakura, Degani and Docklands Pizzeria. You’re also near Southern Cross Station and 70 and 86 tram routes will also take you all over Melbourne.
Insights: 233/117 Studio Lane, Docklands VIC 3008 was last sold in 2017 and 2 other 2 bedroom house in Docklands have recently been sold.

Description:
Unsurpassed Luxury Meets Unbeatable Location
This three/four bedroom townhouse in an ideal location moments from the city and the water's edge alike features spectacular views and offers an additional self-contained ground-floor unit which presents great flexibility as an ideal 4th bedroom, home office, guest accommodation or Airbnb option. Behind its attractive and modern façade this immaculate residence provides exceptional interior spaces split over three levels with finishes of the finest quality.
With outlooks that boast its premier position, the open-plan living and dining zone is complemented by dual balconies plus a barbeque entertainment area that look toward the Melbourne Star and Yarra river. Take the short 100m walk to the rivers edge and embrace unbeatable 180 degree views of the city. An epicurean kitchen enhances the family living area, with European stainless steel appliances, stone countertops and a feature island bench. Three bedrooms are spacious and comprise built-in robes, light-filled interiors and are positioned to embrace desirable north-facing views, and the main bedroom is accompanied by a luxury ensuite with a double vanity. Additional features include two separate study alcoves which could function as open home office spaces or entertainment zones, a double lock up garage, separate laundry and the independent unit comprises a large bedroom/home office, kitchenette, bathroom and its own private carpark.
In a perfectly convenient location this abode is just moments from the CBD, Docklands Harbour, Etihad Stadium, Crown Casino, Sandridge beach, easy freeway access and nearby transport options such as buses at the doorstep, the proposed new Docklands ferry stop and trams within the free tram zone are just a short stroll away. Nearby schools include Port Melbourne Primary School, Albert Park College, Haileybury and Melbourne Grammar School. As part of the of the Mirvac residences, this abode presents resident-only access to gym facilities, entertainment hubs and a selection of cosmopolitan restaurants and cafes.
Insights: 158 Lorimer Street, Docklands VIC 3008 was last sold in 2015 and 2 other 4 bedroom house in Docklands have recently been sold.

Description:
Brand New Penthouse on the City’s Edge
Placed high on the 30th floor of the brand new Forge Apartments complex, this resplendent, spacious, and utterly modern three bedroom, two bathroom Docklands Penthouse promises dazzling views of the Yarra River and city skyline as well as two secure car spaces.
It’s easy to see why properties in the Forge complex have quickly become some of the hottest commodities in the entire Docklands area. Filled with elegance and grace, this contemporary delight shows off with relaxed lounge and dining which features wonderful water and CBD views, as does the sizeable undercover balcony ideal for alfresco dining.
An integrated fridge and freezer, designer cabinetry, stone benchtops, and Smeg appliances define the gourmet kitchen, meanwhile all bedrooms are equipped with built-in robes and floor-to-ceiling windows including the master bedroom which also delivers a private ensuite. A study nook, pristine bathroom, and separate laundry are other highlights.
Together with heating and cooling, video intercom, and the two car spaces, you also have access to the Wharf’s Club with gym, pool and café as well as a private kitchen/dining room and cinema.
Enjoy the wonderful Yarra’s Edge precinct where you’ll be near restaurants including Citizen Café and Bar, Melbourne Public, Bangpop, and Munich Brauhaus just to name a few. You also have easy access to the Victoria Harbour precinct as well Crown Entertainment Complex with world class restaurants, Port Melbourne and South Melbourne attractions, and Southern Cross Station.

Description:
Elegant Style with Enviable Water Views
Perfectly placed in one of the Docklands most exclusive complexes, The Quays, this beautifully-appointed and relaxed one bedroom residence embodies modern apartment living that is sure to captivate CBD professionals, first home buyers, and smart investors.
A formal entrance hall takes you directly into the central living and meals zone which boasts floor-to-ceiling windows which opens out to the balcony overlooking the communal garden, tennis courts and Victoria Harbour, an idyllic spot to breathe in the fresh air and enjoy alfresco dining.
The designer kitchen is fitted with stainless steel appliances including a dishwasher and the stylish bathroom with vibrant mosaic wall tiles includes a European laundry. With reverse cycle cooling, secure intercom, and a secure car space this apartment has everything you need for low maintenance apartment living.
The sensational Quays complex offers a Health Club with a swimming pool, spa, sauna, gymnasium and a yoga studio, while there is a Resident’s Club on Level One with a library, reading room, business centre, boardroom, private dining room & cinema lounge. Further enjoy a rooftop garden with tennis court, BBQ and dining facilities.
The NewQuay precinct is a lively hub and home to some of the Docklands best attractions. Trams will take you over all over Melbourne including the MCG, Richmond, Hawthorn, and Box Hill, while surrounding restaurants cover cuisines of all types. You’re also moments to Harbour Town Shopping Centre, Medibank Icehouse, Costco, Melbourne Star Observation Wheel, and the iconic Festival Hall.

Description:
Live The Docklands Dream With Inspired CBD Views
Graced with a fabulous NewQuay precinct edge while offering spacious and well-appointed living with sensational views of the CBD and Victoria Harbour, this two bedroom, two bathroom 18th floor residence is truly exceptional.
Whether you’re relaxing inside on a chilly winter’s evening or enjoying the summer sun on the fantastic outdoor spaces, this inspired Docklands oasis will have owner-occupiers and investors eager to buy. Two separate balconies allow for stellar areas to dine and partake in weekend drinks, with the large main alfresco area enjoying memorable city and water vistas.
The 2nd balcony can be accessed via the generous master bedroom which is complete with walk-in robes and ensuite, meanwhile the other bedroom has BIR and is directly opposite the stylish bathroom. The spacious central lounge and dining has open living in mind and is adjoined by a designer stone with breakfast bar and stainless steel appliances, while appreciate a separate laundry, ducted heating and cooling, secure intercom, storage cage, secure car space and access to a pool, gym and entertaining area.
Enjoy all the amenities and attractions of this excellent location close to Waterfront City, Harbour Town Shopping Centre, Melbourne Star Observation Wheel and Costco. You also have trams running out to Bundoora RMIT and the CBD, while nearby restaurants include Docklands Pizzeria, Aree Thai Restaurant, and Renzo’s Bar Café Italiano, just to name a few.
Please contact Clare Thompson on 0474 044 293 to arrange an exclusive viewing.

Breathtaking Penthouse Views and Modern Flair
Checking off all the things you’re looking for in a luxury Docklands apartment including chic and elegant style, marina views and a stunning location in the Yarra’s Edge precinct, this north-facing Penthouse is simply perfect.
This impressive riverside pad is an ideal choice for city workers, keen owner-occupiers or those looking for an investment property. The apartment is located in the highly desirable Yarra’s Edge hub and presents a spacious central living and dining zone which opens through sliding floor-to-ceiling windows to a tiled undercover balcony where you will be charmed by views of the bordering marina. Back inside, the contemporary kitchen enjoys a sleek black colour scheme and features stainless steel appliances.
The bedroom is well-sized and offers up ample built-in robe storage, meanwhile the bathroom fits in with the theme of sumptuous style. Description:
Dock 5 – Spacious Home with a Lifestyle
Well renowned architect, John Wardle has certainly set the platform for the stunning design of Dock 5, for other developments to compete. Featuring sculptural form, folding glass of the exterior and the internal artistic attributes of the foyer, this remarkable masterpiece could not be complete without the highest quality finishes and fixtures.
As you enter the front door of this level 13th floor 3 bedroom residence, you know you will be stepping into an amazing dwelling.
On the right wing of the apartment, two bedrooms with built in robes are serviced by the central stylish bathroom with laundry facilities. To the left, the large main bedroom, with a full ensuite, features a full length built in robes.
The best is yet to come. As you journey forward, budding chefs will be drawn towards the spacious kitchen, offering plenty of preparation space and a walk in pantry.
In keeping with the Nautical theme of Dock 5, the dining living room opens up like a giant oyster shell revealing spectacular pearl quality panoramic views, encompassing the marina, the You Yang ranges to the north and to amazing sunsets to the West.
Sit back and relax on the long wrap balcony and enjoy from the spectacular New Year's fireworks.
Other features of the apartment include:
- Reverse cycle ducted heating and cooling
- Gas and water outlet on the balcony - perfect for BBQ's and your own private garden
- Dual drawer dishwashing machine
- Motorised blinds in the living dining area and main bedroom
- Wine cabinet in temperature controlled room
- Indoor swimming pool, gymnasium
- 2 side by side car spaces
- Security entrance, garage remote access
- On site manager
- Separate ding area

Description:
Elegant Harbor Town Living!
Just upstairs from the cosmopolitan Harbour town shops, set upon a quiet rooftop, this townhouse with Japanese-inspired contemporary design provides space-saving luxury. The kitchen, with stainless steel fittings, huge pantry space and dishwasher; and the living area are flooded with light by two large glass sliding doors to either side, one which leads to the private balcony, the other a private terrace. Upstairs two bedrooms, with a choice of a view of either the beautiful communal gardens, or the Harbour town community. The upstairs bathroom, with large, glass door shower, completes the picture, only a few minutes' walk from the Melbourne Star and all the public transport.

Description:
Amazing Views and Striking Watergate Style
Displaying sensational westerly views which take in the neighbouring Docklands Park as well as out to the tranquil waters of Port Phillip Bay, this excellent 105 sq.m approx. two bedroom, two bathroom Watergate apartment will captivate all with its contemporary elegance and standout Victoria Harbour location.
Inside this 15th floor retreat you can enjoy memorable views from the expansive central living zone which promises specific lounge and dining spaces, as well as the full-length undercover balcony. The immaculate kitchen just off the entry is another major highlight delivering a stainless steel breakfast bar and appliances.
Both bedrooms come with their own unique advantages. The master bedroom enjoys a walk-in robe and private ensuite, while the 2nd bedroom has a built-in robe and study nook. Also embrace a stylish bathroom with laundry, central heating and cooling, video intercom entry, secure car space, and access to facilities including a pool, sauna, and gym.
The amazing harbour precinct offers the convenience of the CBD just a short walk away, as well as access to terrific eateries including The Hof Downtown, The Spice Dine, and Twirled Pasta Bar just to name a few. You’re also right near The Hub @ Docklands, Etihad Stadium, Woolworths Victoria Harbour, and trams on Harbour Esplanade.
Please call Clare Thompson on 0474 044 293 to arrange an exclusive viewing.
